---
title: Carb Smart Sesame-Crusted Tofu Salad with Avocado and Creamy Sesame Dressing
description: Seared tofu, coated in sesame seeds, sits on top fresh spinach, avocado and tomato salad. But the best part of this tasty dish is the nutty, craveable sesame dressing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1026_W22_CA_RC162301-1_MAIN_low-bc22c9f8.jpg
